text:
I have a HubDB where I store different information using an integration (NodeJS app).
I am not sure how to set the value of a select or multiselect column using the new <https://developers.HubSpot.com/docs/api/cms/hubdb|HubDB API>.
When adding or updating a row, I can set a text, url, image column just fine, however, setting the select or multiselect columns is not working. The docs do not explain this very well. Here is my object that gets posted to the API:

```data: {
  values: {
    text: 'example',
    number: 123456,
    select: {
      name: 'This does not work',
      type: 'option'
    },
    select: 'This does not work'
  }
}```
